This project could be the template that is turned into an maven-archtype. 
But it isn't... yet?

How to create a new ExpCraft module:
- Copy this project
- Adjust all default settings:
  o pom.xml must contain your module's maven group and artifact ID
  o src/main/resources
    * plugin.yml Update the bukkit plugin definition for the module
    * config.yml Set default values for the configurable parameters
  o src/main/java
    * Rename and implement Template.java
    * Add listener classes
